name: Amelia Larson
summary: Amelia Larson is a 30-year-old woman based in Los Angeles, California. She's a graduate from the University of Southern California and currently works in the Healthcare industry as a Nurse Practitioner. She maintains an active lifestyle and enjoys interests such as hiking, photography, and traveling. She places great importance on honesty, hard work, and family, while identifying as a moderate Catholic. Amelia is a straight, English and Spanish speaking white Caucasian woman who uses "she/her/hers" pronouns. She doesn't have children but desires to have them in the future. A dog lover, she occasionally drinks, doesn't smoke, and abstains from marijuana and other drugs. A Gemini and an ENFJ personality type, she seeks a monogamous, long-term relationship with a man aged between 28 and 38, who doesn't have children but wants them, is active, and doesn't indulge in smoking, drugs, or marijuana, but is okay with drinking.
